title: bremer-media - Community Sponsor of PyCon DE & PyData
---
full_description: bremer-media is a freelance project from Klaus Bremer. Originated from a scientific background with experience in informatics and programming scientific solutions, later there have been tasks in advertising and publishing. Python experience started about 1999 and today industrial customers and agencies get support for non standard solutions, often web-related, from automation up to machine learning. This includes advanced web-hosting setup in combination with specialized hosting companies. Additionally customized Python trainings in cooperation with the python-academy are provided. 

